These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, tea, milk, soy-milk, sprite, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, techno, trance, jazz, country, metal
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: golf, swimming, coffee-polo, basketball, snowboarding, surfing, handball
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, roller, helicopter, snowmobile, boat, subway, quad-bike
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 3. the person driving the airplane is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 5. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the fan of country##1
 7. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 9. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
10. the fan of techno is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
12. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
13. the fan of jazz is in the middle##1
14. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is coffee-polo##1
15. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
16. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
17. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
18. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
19. the person driving the helicopter is in the middle##1
20. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
21. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Beverage      | milk    | mirinda     | coffee  | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk | sprite      | tea          |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | trance   | country  | jazz       | dubstep  | hip-hop      | techno     |
| Sport         | golf | swimming | snowboarding | surfing | coffee-polo   | basketball     | handball |
| Transport     | quad-bike      | subway   | airplane   | helicopter  | snowmobile  | boat | roller       |

